high_descs: turn left and stop before the sink and turn to face the counter to the right of the sink
pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is to the left of the potted plant
turn to the left, move forward towards the wall and turn to the left to face the long brown table
slice the apple with the knife into three quarters
turn to the left move forward slightly, stop in front of the sink
put the knife into the left side of the sink
turn around to face the brown table in front of the slice apple
pick up one of the slices of the apple
turn around to face the microwave
open the microwave door, put the apple into the microwave, close the door and cook the apple for three seconds, open the door and remove the apple slice
turn to face the sink
put the slice of apple into the sink to the left of the knife with the yellow handle
anns.task_desc: put a slice of cooked apple into the sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the kitchen counter with a plant on the right.
Pick up the knife next to the plant.
Turn left, go towards the wall, turn left to face the table.
Use the knife to slice the apple into three.
Turn around and head towards the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and head back to the table.
Pick up the right piece of the sliced apple.
Turn left, go towards the sink, turn around to face the wall.
Open the microwave on the right side, place apple in, close the door and turn on microwave. Wait until microwave stops and take apple out.
Turn left and walk up, turn right and walk up, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, then face right to see the counter top with the flower.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle
Move left to the far wall and bring the knife to the wooden table to behind the counter top.
slice the apple into three slices
walk with the knife back to the counter top with the sink on top.
place the knife in the left part of the sink
return to the wooden table with the sliced apple
pick up one piece of the sliced apple
turn around and face the microwave directly behind you
open the microwave, place the apple inside for a few seconds, then remove the apple slice.
move the apple slice to the sink to the left of the microwave
place the apple in the sink to the left of the knife
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple with a knife, heat one slice, and return everything to the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right to the counter to the right of the sink.
Take the large knife from the counter.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the brown table.
Cut the red apple closest to the wall into pieces.
Turn around, go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the brown table.
Take the a piece of apple from the brown table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left to the sink, go to the sink, turn right.
Cook the apple in the microwave on the right, then take the apple out.
Turn right and go to the area between the sink and the counter on the left.
Put the piece of apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of cooked apple in a sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward to the counter on the right where the plant is.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is on the counter by the plant.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn left to face the table.
Cut the apple that is on the table.
Turn to the left, go forward to the sink that is on the left.
Put the knife in to the sink.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, turn left to face the table.
Pick up a slice of the apple from the table.
Back up, turn to the left, go forward, turn around,
Put the apple in the microwave and turn it on to cook, take the apple out of the microwave when it is done cooking.
Back up, turn to the left, go forward, turn to the right, go forward to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink to the left of the yellow handled knife.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked apple into the sink.

high_descs: Move slightly to stand in front of the counter directly to the right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter, which is by the plant.
Carry the knife to the closest end of the long wooden table.
Slice the apple on the table with the knife.
Carry the knife to stand at the counter to the left of the kitchen sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn and move back to the end of the wooden table, facing the sliced apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the table.
Carry the slice of apple to stand in front of the kitchen sink, facing the microwave, which is to the left of the sink.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, turn it on, and then remove once heated.
Move to stand facing the counter between the microwave and sink, holding the apple slice.
Place the apple slice in the sink to the left of the sharp knife you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of apple in the kitchen sink.
